            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/R2344Step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>coriander</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Add the <strong>chopped coriander</strong> to the zingy apple slaw and give everything a good mix up</span></p>\n<p>Remove most of the leaves from the <strong>baby gem lettuce<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> and set aside</p>\n<p>Shred the<strong> inner core</strong></p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
